      <title>俄罗斯制裁导致运费上涨，油运贸易商蜂拥入市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/oil-freight-traders-pile-in-as-russia-sanctions-push-rates-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于拜登政府对俄罗斯的制裁继续推高超级油轮运价，石油运费衍生品交易飙升至至少十年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/oil-freight-traders-pile-in-as-russia-sanctions-push-rates-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 17:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
