    <item>
      <title>原糖因供应前景改善而创下四个月新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/cocoa-gains-as-lindt-s-strong-sales-signal-demand-resilience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场适应主要种植国巴西、印度和泰国更为光明的供应前景，原糖期货跌至四个月新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/cocoa-gains-as-lindt-s-strong-sales-signal-demand-resilience</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 14:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
